  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <h3>Features</h3>
      <ul class="styled">
        <li>Highly customizable and extensible.</li>
        <li>Rich with features - add legends, labels, tooltips, and
        mouseover effects.</li>
        <li>Robust & polished - weird data will not cause your charts to
        break.</li>
        <li>Roll your own charts by extending our ChartComponent class -
        get labels, automatic resizing, and reasonable defaults for
        margins, padding, etc.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <h3>Dependencies</h3>
      <ul class="styled">
        <li><a href="https://d3js.org/">D3.js</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://emberjs.com/">Ember.js</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://lodash.com/">Lo-Dash.js</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://jquery.com/">jQuery</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://jqueryui.com/">jQuery UI</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
